{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew already then that there is what you call a lot of 'tsuris.' And-- and they said we have to be in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, our house, our street, was fenced in-- part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we felt very fortunate that we don't have to get out of our own home, because people who lived in very comfortable homes had to move in with families where they got one room for a whole family, and it was very cramped and very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, if I may say this, I have a memory of a very dear friend that perished in the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Her-- after we had moved out of that beautiful home that I described, my-- a rabbi moved in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A rabbi and his family lived there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the daughter was my friend-- a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had to move out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were across the street from us, but our side stayed in the ghetto, and they had to move out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember another friend telling me that she is sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She is very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was always a very, very pretty, tall, blonde, very slim little girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so we went through the backyards, in order to go visit her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember coming in to a very dingy room where she was sleeping on a-- laying on a mattress.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember her mother being so grateful that we came to see her and saying that she  is sick.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the last I saw her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I found out that she never made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
